Rasul JENKINS, a/k/a Rasool Jacobs, Rasul Jacobs, Rasool Jenkins, Money Bags, and Roy Simmins, Appellant-Petitioner,
v.
NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, Respondent-Respondent. C-162 September Term 2018
081161 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 5, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005186-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
